title: You can’t rush a Biscay breakthrough in marine energy
description: Yago Torre-Enciso of BiMEP says that patience and persistence will be essential to achieving commercial-scale marine energy, a milestone he doesn’t expect to see before 2050.
content: Yago Torre-Enciso of BiMEP says that patience and persistence will be essential to achieving commercial-scale marine energy, a milestone he doesn’t expect to see before 2050.
